data.description: Come see this charming 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home with a new roof! The outside features a classic brick look all around with a well-manicured front lawn. The private backyard has plenty of space and lots of vegetation, framed in by nice shrubs and bushes. Inside, you'll find a tiled entry way, leading into a large, open, living room; equipped with new flooring and beautiful French doors leading out onto the back porch. The kitchen features an isolated island and a nice open look of the living room; perfect for entertaining while you cook! A spacious, split floor plan, a separate laundry room, and over 1700 square feet make this home a must see!
